# Luminary Wishes — Redirect Rules (Netlify / Cloudflare Pages)

# Canonical domain — redirect www to non-www
https://www.luminarywishes.dpdns.org/* https://luminarywishes.dpdns.org/:splat 301!

# Short wish links → templates
/b/:token   /templates/birthday.html?token=:token    200
/a/:token   /templates/anniversary.html?token=:token  200
/m/:token   /templates/marriage.html?token=:token     200

# Legacy URL redirects
/privacy    /more/privacy.html    301
/terms      /more/terms.html      301
/owner      /more/owner.html      301
/credits    /more/credits.html    301

# 404 fallback
/*  /404.html  404
